Package: HLAhaploTools
Title: Tools for Inference and Analysis of Extended HLA Haplotypes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Fredrick", "Mobegi", email = "fredrick.mobegi@health.wa.gov.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for working with extended human leukocyte antigen (HLA) haplotypes, including functions for haplotype construction, visualization, family-based inference, and population-level summaries. Supports both classical and non-classical HLA loci, as well as MICA and MICB genes. Facilitates multi-locus haplotype analysis for use in immunogenetics, transplantation matching, and genetic association studies.
